      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   prn-tst-max-000      thru prn-tst-max-999        .
           if        w-cnt-prn-flg-sub    not  = spaces
                     move   spaces        to   w-cnt-prn-flg-sub
                     go to  prn-rou-pri-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
