           move      w-bak-des-bak        to   rr-des-bak             .
           perform   vis-des-bak-000      thru vis-des-bak-999        .
       acc-cod-bak-490.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tipo unita' da utilizzare               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-bak-tip-dev        to   rr-tip-dev             .
           perform   vis-tip-dev-000      thru vis-tip-dev-999        .
       acc-cod-bak-495.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
